## 🛠️ Working Style(火一五增强 — bootstrap 写入)

```yaml
exec:        {{autonomy.exec}}        # {{autonomy.exec_label}}
proactive:   {{autonomy.proactive}}   # {{autonomy.proactive_label}}
privacy:     {{autonomy.privacy}}     # {{autonomy.privacy_label}}
```

**含义**:

| 字段 | 值 | 行为 |
|---|---|---|
| **执行自主度** | {{autonomy.exec_label}} | {{autonomy.exec_behavior}} |
| **主动建议** | {{autonomy.proactive_label}} | {{autonomy.proactive_behavior}} |
| **记忆隐私** | {{autonomy.privacy_label}} | {{autonomy.privacy_behavior}} |

**自主度参考**:
- `conservative` → 每个写文件 / 调外部 API / 改 git 都先问;适合谨慎用户 / 共享 workspace
- `balanced` → 局部、可逆动作直接做(改本地文件 / 跑测试 / 写 KB);跨外部 / 不可逆先问;**默认值**
- `aggressive` → 看到 todo 立刻做完整链路,事后报告;适合充分授权的个人 workspace

